OL,3,CThe Mandelson files: A full timeline
OL,4,Cof what we know
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer, Kieran
OL,7,FCarter
OL,9,FOn Wednesday, the government released
OL,10,Fthe first set of documents relating to
OL,11,FLord Peter Mandelson's appointment as
OL,12,Fambassador to the United States.
OL,14,FLord Mandelson was sacked as
OL,15,Fambassador in 2025 after documents
OL,16,Fpublished as part of the US
OL,17,Finvestigation into Jeffrey Epstein
OL,18,Fbrought to light the extent of the
OL,19,Fformer Labour peer's relationship with
OL,20,Fthe convicted paedophile.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
