OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773302722
OL,3,CThe Mandelson files: A full timeline
OL,4,Cof what we know
OL,6,FDespite admitting to being aware of
OL,7,Fthis relationship, the prime minister
OL,8,Fhas repeatedly insisted Lord Mandelson
OL,9,F"lied repeatedly" to No 10 about the
OL,10,Fextent of his relationship with
OL,11,FEpstein, before and during his tenure
OL,12,Fas ambassador.
OL,14,FHe claimed that if he had known then
OL,15,Fwhat he later found out, Lord
OL,16,FMandelson "would never have been
OL,17,Fanywhere near government."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
