OL,3,CThe Mandelson files: A full timeline
OL,4,Cof what we know
OL,6,FMandelson has since apologised for his
OL,7,Frelationship with Epstein, claiming he
OL,8,Fdid not witness wrongdoing in his
OL,9,Finteractions with the paedophile.
OL,11,FIn relation to his arrest on suspicion
OL,12,Fof misconduct in public office, the
OL,13,Fformer ambassador has claimed not to
OL,14,Fhave acted in any way criminally and
OL,15,Fthat he was not motivated by financial
OL,16,Fgain.
OL,18,FThe documents' release comes after MPs
OL,19,Fforced the government to publish them
OL,20,Fin an effort to achieve greater
OL,21,Ftransparency.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/23
