OL,3,CThe Mandelson files: A full timeline
OL,4,Cof what we know
OL,6,FITV News explores the timeline of
OL,7,Fevents that led to these documents'
OL,8,Frelease.
OL,10,F2003 - Messages from Mandelson to
OL,11,FEpstein are included in a 50th
OL,12,Fbirthday book compiled for the
OL,13,Fdisgraced financier, and released by
OL,14,Fthe Department of Justice.
OL,16,FSeveral pages in this book show photos
OL,17,Fof Mandelson with Epstein, accompanied
OL,18,Fby handwritten messages in which the
OL,19,Fformer ambassador calls Epstein his
OL,20,F"best pal".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
