OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773302722
OL,3,CThe Mandelson files: A full timeline
OL,4,Cof what we know
OL,6,FWhile the book was gifted in 2003, it
OL,7,Fwas only released by the Department of
OL,8,FJustice in July last year.
OL,10,F2003 & June 2004 - Bank statements
OL,11,Fappear to show Epstein made several
OL,12,Fpayments totalling $25,000 (#56,000)
OL,13,Fto accounts associated with Lord
OL,14,FMandelson.
OL,16,FIt is unclear what these are in
OL,17,Frelation to, and when they were
OL,18,Fbrought to light. Mandelson claimed
OL,19,Fnot to recall them, calling into
OL,20,Fquestion whether they were genuine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
