OL,3,CThe Mandelson files: A full timeline
OL,4,Cof what we know
OL,6,F2008 - Epstein pleads guilty to
OL,7,Fsoliciting prostitution and soliciting
OL,8,Fa minor and is sentenced to 18 months
OL,9,Fin prison.
OL,11,FOn the eve of his arrest, Lord
OL,12,FMandelson sends emails to Epstein
OL,13,Furging him to "fight for early
OL,14,Frelease", and promises: "Your friends
OL,15,Fstay with you and love you."
OL,17,FJune 2009 - Mandelson stays at
OL,18,FEpstein's New York apartment while the
OL,19,Fconvicted sex offender is serving his
OL,20,F18-month prison sentence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
