OL,3,CThe Mandelson files: A full timeline
OL,4,Cof what we know
OL,6,FSeptember 2009 - Emails appear to show
OL,7,FMandelson's husband, Reinaldo Avila da
OL,8,FSilva, thanking Epstein for a payment
OL,9,Fof #10,000 to fund an osteopathy
OL,10,Fcourse.
OL,12,FDecember 15, 2009 - An email
OL,13,Fcorrespondence between Lord Mandelson,
OL,14,Fthen business secretary in Gordon
OL,15,FBrown's government, and Epstein shows
OL,16,Fthe financier asking if a policy
OL,17,Fannounced one week earlier to tax
OL,18,Fbankers' bonuses could be changed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
