OL,3,CThe Mandelson files: A full timeline
OL,4,Cof what we know
OL,6,FLord Mandelson appeared to reply:
OL,7,F"Trying hard to amend as I explained
OL,8,Fto Jes last night. Treasury digging in
OL,9,Fbut I am on case.
OL,11,F"They are not being helpful."
OL,13,FEpstein then asked Mandelson who he
OL,14,Fmeant, to which the former Labour peer
OL,15,Fresponded: the "Treasury".
OL,17,FMay 9, 2010 - Emails appear to show
OL,18,FMandelson giving Epstein advance
OL,19,Fnotice of an EU E500 billion bailout
OL,20,Fto save the Euro.
OL,26,@{D@QOk
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/23
