OL,3,CThe Mandelson files: A full timeline
OL,4,Cof what we know
OL,6,FJuly 6 2019 - Epstein is arrested in
OL,7,FNew York on sex trafficking charges.
OL,8,FHe is found dead in his cell one month
OL,9,Flater, having taken his own life.
OL,11,FDecember 2024 - Starmer declared he
OL,12,Fwas "delighted to appoint" Mandelson
OL,13,Fas UK ambassador to the US, saying
OL,14,F"Peter will bring unrivalled
OL,15,Fexperience to the role."
OL,17,FFeb 10, 2025 - Lord Mandelson begins
OL,18,Fhis tenure in Washington as the UK's
OL,19,Fambassador.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
