OL,3,CThe Mandelson files: A full timeline
OL,4,Cof what we know
OL,6,FSeptember 9, 2025 - The US House
OL,7,FOversight Committee releases documents
OL,8,Fshowing messages and photos compiled
OL,9,Fin a book for Epstein's 50th birthday,
OL,10,Fwhich includes messages from Mandelson
OL,11,Freferring to the paedophile as his
OL,12,F"best pal", suggesting a much closer
OL,13,Frelationship between the pair than had
OL,14,Fpreviously been believed.
OL,16,FSeptember 10 2025 - Mandelson gives an
OL,17,Finterview to The Sun, in which he
OL,18,Fexpresses regret for continuing his
OL,19,Frelationship with Epstein for so long
OL,20,Fand suggests further embarrassing
OL,21,Fcorrespondence was likely to come out.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
