OL,3,CThe Mandelson files: A full timeline
OL,4,Cof what we know
OL,6,FSeptember 11, 2025 - Mandelson is
OL,7,Fremoved as ambassador.
OL,9,FThe Foreign Office stated that emails
OL,10,Fshowing the extent of Mandelson's
OL,11,Frelationship with Epstein were
OL,12,F"materially different from that known
OL,13,Fat the time of his appointment."
OL,15,FJanuary 11, 2026 - In an interview
OL,16,Fwith the BBC's Laura Kuenssberg,
OL,17,FMandelson claims to have never seen
OL,18,Fgirls at Epstein's properties.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
