OL,3,CThe Mandelson files: A full timeline
OL,4,Cof what we know
OL,6,FMandelson claimed to believe he had
OL,7,Fbeen "kept separate" from Epstein's
OL,8,Fsexual encounters on account of being
OL,9,Fa gay man.
OL,11,FPushed on whether he would apologise
OL,12,Ffor his relationship, he refused to do
OL,13,Fso.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
