OL,3,CThe Mandelson files: A full timeline
OL,4,Cof what we know
OL,6,FJanuary 12, 2026 - Mandelson goes
OL,7,Ffurther, issuing an apology to the
OL,8,FBBC's Newsnight in which he said : "I
OL,9,Fwas wrong to believe him following his
OL,10,Fconviction and to continue my
OL,11,Fassociation with him afterwards. I
OL,12,Fapologise unequivocally for doing so
OL,13,Fto the women and girls who suffered."
OL,15,FFebruary 1, 2026 - Lord Mandelson
OL,16,Fresigns from the Labour Party after
OL,17,Fallegations he received payments from
OL,18,FEpstein are brought to light.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
