OL,3,CThe Mandelson files: A full timeline
OL,4,Cof what we know
OL,6,FAt the time, he said he had no
OL,7,Frecollection of receiving these
OL,8,Fpayments and did not know if the
OL,9,Fdocuments showing them were genuine.
OL,11,FFebruary 4, 2026 - Starmer admitted
OL,12,Fduring PMQ's he knew of Mandelson's
OL,13,Ffriendship with Epstein, but said his
OL,14,Fformer colleague had "lied repeatedly
OL,15,Fto my team... before and during his
OL,16,Ftenure as ambassador."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
