OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773302722
OL,3,CThe Mandelson files: A full timeline
OL,4,Cof what we know
OL,6,FHe said. "Mandelson betrayed our
OL,7,Fcountry, our parliament, and my party.
OL,8,FI regret appointing him. If I knew
OL,9,Fthen what I know now, he would never
OL,10,Fhave been anywhere near government."
OL,12,FAsked in parliament whether vetting
OL,13,Fcarried out before Lord Mandelson's
OL,14,Fappointment had included his ongoing
OL,15,Frelationship with Epstein, Starmer
OL,16,Freplied: "Yes, it did."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
