OL,3,CThe Mandelson files: A full timeline
OL,4,Cof what we know
OL,6,FFebruary 4, 2026 - MPs vote to force
OL,7,Fthe government to release all
OL,8,FMandelson files after the
OL,9,FConservatives file a motion compelling
OL,10,Fthe government to do so.
OL,12,FBacklash from Labour MPs led by an
OL,13,Fintervention from former Deputy PM
OL,14,FAngela Rayner forced the government to
OL,15,Fclimb down on a decision to block the
OL,16,Frelease of files deemed a national
OL,17,Fsecurity risk.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/23
