OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773302722
OL,3,CThe Mandelson files: A full timeline
OL,4,Cof what we know
OL,6,F"What has come to light has raised
OL,7,Fserious questions. Information that
OL,8,Fwas not known at the time of his
OL,9,Fappointment. Before he was appointed
OL,10,Fambassador, Mandelson was asked
OL,11,Fdirectly about his relationship with
OL,12,FEpstein. He was asked whether he had
OL,13,Fstayed with Epstein after his
OL,14,Fconviction.
OL,16,F"And when, later, further information
OL,17,Fcame to light... He was asked whether
OL,18,Fhe had accepted gifts and hospitality,
OL,19,Fabout whether he had been fully
OL,20,Ftransparent about the relationship.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31620
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773302722
OL,3,CThe Mandelson files: A full timeline
OL,4,Cof what we know
OL,6,F"The information now available makes
OL,7,Fclear that the answers he gave were
OL,8,Flies. He had portrayed Epstein as
OL,9,Fsomeone he barely knew. And when that
OL,10,Fbecame clear and it was not true, I
OL,11,Fsacked him."
OL,13,FFebruary 23, 2026 - Mandelson is
OL,14,Farrested on suspicion of misconduct in
OL,15,Fpublic office.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
