OL,3,CThe Mandelson files: A full timeline
OL,4,Cof what we know
OL,6,FResponding to the arrest, a lawyer
OL,7,Frepresenting Mandelson issued a
OL,8,Fstatement claiming: "The arrest was
OL,9,Fprompted by a baseless suggestion that
OL,10,Fhe was planning to leave the country
OL,11,Fand take up permanent residence
OL,12,Fabroad. There is absolutely no truth
OL,13,Fwhatsoever in any such suggestion."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
